					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="project-card">
				<div class="project-image">
					<img 
						src="/images/projects/dashboard-analytics.jpg"
						alt="GymApp - App de seguimiento de entrenamientos"
						class="project-img"
						loading="lazy"
						onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
					/>
					<div class="image-fallback" style="display: none;">
						<div class="fallback-content">
							<svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="12" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
								<circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/>
								<path d="M21 15L16 10L5 21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
							</svg>
							<p>GymApp</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="project-overlay">
						<div class="overlay-content">
							<h4>GymApp</h4>
							<p>Seguimiento de entrenamientos</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="project-content">
					<div class="project-header">
						<h3>GymApp</h3>
						<span class="project-status-badge in-progress">En Desarrollo</span>
					</div>
					<p class="project-description">
						Aplicación móvil para el seguimiento de entrenamientos, creación de rutinas personalizadas, 
						monitoreo de progreso físico y estadísticas detalladas de rendimiento.
					</p>
					<div class="project-tech">
						<span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
						<span class="tech-tag">React Native</span>
						<span class="tech-tag">Expo</span>
						<span class="tech-tag">SQLite</span>
					</div>
					<div class="project-links">
						<a href="https://github.com/Meerita4/gymapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">
							<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<path d="M9 19C4 20.5 4 16.5 2 16M22 16C22 16 20 20.5 15 19C15 19 15 18 15 17V14.5C15 13.5 15 13 14 13H12.5C10.5 13 9.5 11.5 9.5 10.5V9C9.5 7.5 10.5 6 12.5 6H14C15 6 15 6.5 15 7.5V9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
							</svg>
							GitHub
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			

			<div class="project-card">
				<div class="project-image">
					<img 
						src="/images/projects/portfolio.jpg" 
						alt="Portfolio Website - Sitio web personal"
						class="project-img"
						loading="lazy"
					/>
					<div class="project-overlay">
						<div class="overlay-content">
							<h4>Portfolio Web</h4>
							<p>Sitio web personal moderno</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="project-content">
					<div class="project-header">
						<h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="project-description">
						Sitio web portfolio responsivo y moderno con animaciones suaves, optimización SEO y 
						rendimiento excepcional. Construido con las últimas tecnologías web.
					</p>
					<div class="project-tech">
						<span class="tech-tag">Astro</span>
						<span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
						<span class="tech-tag">CSS3</span>
						<span class="tech-tag">Vercel</span>
					</div>
					<div class="project-links">
						<a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">
							<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
